MARLOTH PARK &#8211; The body of an unidentified man was found beside a fence in Marloth Park. Const Natacia Mbuyane from Komatipoort SAPS, confirmed that a case had been opened and an investigation into the man&#8217;s death is ongoing. No cause of death, identity or motive for being in that location has been established as yet.Read more: Woman raped in Marloth ParkThe Nkomazi Local Municipality issued a decree on December 23. From that day until further notice, no pedestrians or cyclists will be allowed in Marloth Park between 18:30 and 05:00.This is due to the possibility of dangerous animals and an increase in criminal activity that has been reported over the past few weeks.Transgressors will be arrested immediately and detained by the police for further investigation.